articles.author: Brooke Singman
articles.title: Trump defends himself on the stand, blasts E Jean Carroll trial: 'This is not America' - Fox News
articles.description: Former President Trump took the stand on Thursday in his defense in the civil defamation damages trial stemming from E. Jean Carroll’s defamation lawsuit claiming he sexually attacked her in a department store dressing room in the 1990s.
